                    <span>I have been paging through this book over and over. I wish I had this book when I was working on my project. All the illustrations are available on the CD in full size. Appendix B has a very good insight on an issue that is in this hobby.<P>This hobby is changing so fast that it is hard to keep up the new products and ideas. The book and its accompaning websites help point you in the right direction of the latest products and ideas to help make your project better and unique.</span>
                  
              
